{"tid":814661,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)重裝任務 新特警判官 魔山1-2","createTime":"2018-09-11T11:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T17:55:17.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e32443af9f8d74973c5236853d2e9ea9c9cc729","tid":814661,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=FMEASu643V7aAMZ1LAlKwb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=9bf35be6\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=FMEASu643V7aAMZ1LAlKwb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=0dcc167f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=FMEASu643V7aAMZ1LAlKwb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=60f70de2\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/woosean/4a1a62fe7270d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fwoosean%2F4a1a62fe7270d.jpg&h=8da97ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/16/Dredd2012Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F16%2FDredd2012Poster.jpg&h=966cac5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/lf25166234/1446861913-910787904.png?v=1446861915\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Flf25166234%2F1446861913-910787904.png%3Fv%3D1446861915&h=4d1c4423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在利瑞亞這個國家，人們都是和平相處。利瑞亞系統的規則很簡單，就是：假如你快樂，你會被逮捕；假你哭泣流淚，法律會讓你萬劫不復；如果你閱讀傳誦列為違禁品的書籍圖畫，將是法律重罪。還有，不乖乖吃藥，你也將生命不保。<br />\n這是《重裝任務》裡令人驚愕的未來世界模型，這是一部鋒利的動作驚悚片，背景設定在未來，在那個時空下所有的情緒波動都被當成戰爭和犯罪的根源，於是被嚴格禁止。為了維護和平，每個公民每天要服用固定劑量的「普羅寧」，這種效力強大的藥，被設計來封鎖人類的感覺，讓每個人的喜怒哀樂停滯麻木。假如拒絕服藥的話，會有類似日本武士一樣的特別警察小組，身著制服將你捕殺..<br />\n<br />\n2.未來，美國變成了一片人稱詛咒之地的反烏托邦荒原，受到核輻射的嚴重污染。位於東海岸的超級城市一號中生活有8億居民，是一個暴力叢生的超級大都市，平均每天都會報告1.7萬起犯罪事件。這裡新出現了一種名為「慢動作」的毒品，可以讓人感知到的時間減慢到正常水平的1%。城中唯一用於維持秩序的公權力叫「判官」，擁有法官、陪審團和行刑人三種權力於一身。首席判官把新招募的判官卡珊德拉&middot;安德森交給判官爵德做評估，安德森擁有強大的精神能力，可以感知他人的思想和情緒，但她沒能通過法官的能力傾向測試..<br />\n<br />\n3.警探鮑伯帶著妻子愛絲打算到加州搭遊輪慶祝結婚週年，同行的有小女兒布蘭達、兒子巴比，大女兒琳恩、女婿道格，以及兩人剛出生的小嬰兒，與兩隻牧羊犬，這趟全家出遊的溫馨之旅，所有人因為漫長的公路旅程感到不耐煩&hellip;大鮑伯聽從加油站老工人的意見，決定繞道穿越新墨西哥沙漠，沒想到車子出了問題，一家人進退不得，無情的太陽曬烤著一望無際的沙漠&hellip;受困荒涼地帶的他們，正愁孤立無援..<br />\n<br />\n4.兩年前，美國一家人橫越新墨西哥州「16區」沙漠離奇失蹤的恐怖事件，並未就此平息。一群美國國民兵為運送軍備再次來到了16區，殊不知在眼前的這座「魔山」裡，住著一群受到核能輻射汙染的基因突變人，他們正隔著山覬覦醞釀著更凶殘的殺戮計畫，要讓誤闖魔山禁地的人個個不得&quot;好&quot;死...<br />\n<br />\n8 35PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=FMEASu643V7aAMZ1LAlKwb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7e2216ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=FMEASu643V7aAMZ1LAlKwb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c81b6c57\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73aca74579e84c8461e3e69705e5fd6afd185d3","tid":814661,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de01aac3298b16f9dd98ed91cb2431c6c8dc717e","tid":814661,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef982b288fe87a9ebad9a80e4aa939f59fcb931","tid":814661,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6750670e1dfab38ec2c42b517556e676b2dc6d8b","tid":814661,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b366a4b924313298665b5447824ec81adc7848","tid":814661,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8deec31ef282113db50aadbf1d8b7e5c35d2f17c","tid":814661,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f9dd5c6cd63144b9ff217f360cc6e7172f7293","tid":814661,"uid"